{"tid":1069760,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日Pantry有兩條毒撚為左個飯盒係度嘈嘈閉","createTime":"2019-03-20T07:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T07:45:28.000Z","uid":107362,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa10d9004644dd6f596369b9e6cd8e0b6190df62","tid":1069760,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死 一個叮叮下飯無端端走左去<br />\n一個見人地叮完個飯又唔幫人擺返好d<br />\n<br />\n第一個毒撚返來又唔敢問人做咩個飯盒擺左出黎<br />\n第二個毒撚又唔敢同人解釋<br />\n<br />\n第一個毒撚即刻嬲到掉左人地個飯盒<br />\n跟住攞部手機出黎係咁打字唔知打乜春<br />\n第二個又係度打字 我心諗你條友咁撚柒蠢架個飯盒比人掉左仲係度打字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我同佢地條team個super講呢兩條友做埋今個月好啦 嘈9住我嘆咖啡<br />\n<br />\n利申：Department head"},{"pid":"7cfe573661f3674659756bc0351548321efc183a","tid":1069760,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:29:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦=.="},{"pid":"31723732cbcde4b74ceab39ee2ad2516f94a1e9b","tid":1069760,"uid":187072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"原來就係你條ON9報串，頭先我同咗爸爸講，佢話你下個禮拜好執定嘢走<br />\n見你幾十歲廢老，我都唔想令你冇咗份工，不過係你要玩嘢，咁就唔好怪我"},{"pid":"8856c9ccf60da0ff0078a9ac55efde311f3bff78","tid":1069760,"uid":207426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:33:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcd072b1501828fe2594b98d7c9c0a4cc1c217dd","tid":1069760,"uid":207426,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"719d2820dbb7c4754a9829451b0e7b0abcdd7990","tid":1069760,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}